products.name: Older Boy Paisley Print Swim Shorts
products.longDisplayDescription: Whether theyre cannonballing in the deep end, practicing their doggy paddle technique or showing off by swimming lengths, these swim shorts will be sure to carry them through it all! Featuring an elasticated waistband with drawstring details, their intricate paisley print is surely the design cherry on top. With a subtle blue backdrop, they're ideal for wearing alone for water sessions, or simply team them with a vest top and slides for general pool/beachside enjoyment. We see you adding them to the family holiday wish list...

props.title: Swimwear & Beachwear
props.description: Got a family holiday on the horizon? We're here to help with our range of boys swimwear and beachwear. Make sure he hits the water in style with our range of serotonin-inducing boys swim shorts. Available as separates or as swimwear sets, you can opt for bold colours and prints or swimming trunks featuring his fave characters, from super mario to minecraft swimwear. Our range of boys beachwear comes with built-in elasticated and tie-front design features that'll stay put while he ducks and dives in the water. Add on our staple sunglasses and hats, and your little man will be oh-so-stylish and protected from the sun! Complete your [kids holiday clothes](https://www.primark.com/en-gb/r/holiday-shop/kids-holiday-shop) wardrobe with our staple sunglasses, [boys shorts](https://www.primark.com/en-gb/c/kids/boys/boys-clothing/shorts) and [hats](c/kids/boys/boys-accessories/hats-gloves-and-scarves), and your little man will be oh-so-stylish and protected from the sun!
